ProfileName: Jason P. Pumphrey "the movie & music man"
Summary: The doggies seem to dig it!
text:
I gotta review this product because my pooches can't write reviews (if they could I'd be a rich man, haha!)
Our Cavalier King Charles Spaniels seem to like this Beneful Dog Food well enough, not as much as Pedegree, but they do eat it.
